code: import axios from'axios';const baseUrl='/api/persons';const getAll=()=>{return axios.get(baseUrl).then(response=>response.data);};const create=newObject=>{return axios.post(baseUrl,newObject).then(response=>response.data);};const update=(id,newObject)=>{return axios.put(`${baseUrl}/${id}`,newObject).then(response=>response.data);};const deleteEntry=id=>{return axios.delete(`${baseUrl}/${id}`);};export default{getAll,create,update,deleteEntry};
